longBusinessSummary: Svolder AB (publ) operates is a publicly owned investment manager. The firm operates as an investment trust. It invests in the shares of listed small and medium-size companies in Sweden. Svolder AB (publ) was founded in June, 1993 and is based in Stockholm, Sweden.
